text: The George Washington University is a private, coeducational university in Washington, D.C.. The university has about 24,531 students. It was founded on February 9, 1821. The current president of the university is Steven Knapp. ==Sports== The athletics teams of the university are called the Revolutionaries. They have 22 varsity teams and they compete in the Atlantic 10 Conference. ==Other websites== *George Washington University's Official website *George Washington Revolutionaries Official athletics website Category:Atlantic 10 Conference Category:George Washington University Category:1821 establishments in the United States
